protection were both.

00:13:01.030 --> 00:13:04.890
And we felt that the witnesses
made the case that marriage is

00:13:04.890 --> 00:13:06.830
a fundamental right.

00:13:06.830 --> 00:13:08.460
That it is tied to your
life, liberty,

00:13:08.460 --> 00:13:09.970
and pursuit of happiness.

00:13:09.970 --> 00:13:12.680
And that for individuals who
are not allowed access to

00:13:12.680 --> 00:13:15.740
those fundamental rights,
their lives are really

00:13:15.740 --> 00:13:16.420
diminished.

00:13:16.420 --> 00:13:19.340
The quality of your life is
greatly diminished by not

00:13:19.340 --> 00:13:22.280
having the power to say
"I do" as a grown-up.

00:13:22.280 --> 00:13:25.110
It is the most important
decision you make as an adult,

00:13:25.110 --> 00:13:27.120
who you choose to spend
your life with.

00:13:27.120 --> 00:13:31.440
