that during slavery,

00:13:31.440 --> 00:13:35.730
one of the key features, one of
the most important rights

00:13:35.730 --> 00:13:38.170
that the slaves wanted was
the right to marry.

00:13:38.170 --> 00:13:40.990
Because if you don't have the
full force of the phrase "I

00:13:40.990 --> 00:13:45.520
do" as a free person, then you
are not like other people.

00:13:45.520 --> 00:13:47.270
